    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a pyparsing Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>pyparsing</application> module is an alternative approach
to creating and executing simple grammars, vs. the traditional lex/yacc
approach, or the use of regular expressions.  It provides a library of
classes that client code uses to construct the grammar directly in Python
code.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

